metadata.name: Looking At Death
metadata.description:
We will all die one day. This will never be the end of the road. We will always continue to live in the memories of our loved ones that we left behind and with what we did in this world. Our name will forever echo in the vastness of space. It will carry the message of our existence to the farthest lands.

In memory of all the souls who lost their lives in the occupation of Ukraine...
